{"questionId": "a22baf87-f61e-43f7-b868-52cf0e05d234_5", "correctAnswer": "62", "section": "Math", "steps": [{"title": "Substitute the value x = 2", "content": "Replace $x$ with $2$ in $$f(x) = 7x^3 + 6.$$ This gives $$f(2) = 7(2)^3 + 6.$$"}, {"title": "Compute the result", "content": "Simplify: $$f(2) = 7(8) + 6 = 56 + 6 = 62.$$ The answer is <strong>62</strong>."}]}